### Symbol

Every `Symbol()` call returns a **globally unique** primitive value. Two symbols are never equal, even with the same description. Symbols are not enumerated by `for...in` or `Object.keys()` — only `Object.getOwnPropertySymbols()` or `Reflect.ownKeys()` expose them.

```javascript
const s1 = Symbol('id');
const s2 = Symbol('id');
console.log(s1 === s2); // false — always unique

// Symbol.for — shared global registry
const g1 = Symbol.for('app.id');
const g2 = Symbol.for('app.id');
console.log(g1 === g2); // true
```

**Well-known symbols affect built-in language behavior:**

```javascript
// Symbol.iterator — makes object iterable
class Range {
  constructor(start, end) { this.start = start; this.end = end; }
  [Symbol.iterator]() {
    let n = this.start;
    const end = this.end;
    return { next: () => n <= end ? { value: n++, done: false } : { done: true } };
  }
}
console.log([...new Range(1, 3)]); // [1, 2, 3]

// Symbol.toPrimitive — controls type coercion
const money = {
  amount: 42,
  currency: 'USD',
  [Symbol.toPrimitive](hint) {
    if (hint === 'number') return this.amount;
    if (hint === 'string') return `${this.amount} ${this.currency}`;
    return this.amount; // 'default'
  }
};
console.log(+money);        // 42
console.log(`${money}`);    // '42 USD'
console.log(money + 1);     // 43

// Symbol.hasInstance — controls instanceof
class EvenNumber {
  static [Symbol.hasInstance](num) {
    return Number.isInteger(num) && num % 2 === 0;
  }
}
console.log(4 instanceof EvenNumber); // true
console.log(3 instanceof EvenNumber); // false

// Symbol.toStringTag — affects Object.prototype.toString
class MyCollection {
  get [Symbol.toStringTag]() { return 'MyCollection'; }
}
console.log(Object.prototype.toString.call(new MyCollection())); // '[object MyCollection]'
```

**Common trap:** Using Symbol descriptions for equality checks — descriptions are just for debugging. Two `Symbol('id')` are never equal.

**Частая ошибка:** Использовать описание Symbol для проверки равенства — описания только для отладки. Два `Symbol('id')` никогда не равны.

